\subsubsection*{Observed land use/land cover data}
Observed land use/land cover information was obtained from \cite{roy_development_2015}; a dataset providing maps at 100m $\times$ 100m resolution for 1985, 1995 and 2005 derived from multi-temporal satellite data from Landsat, IRS 1C-LISS III and Resourcesat1 instruments. The overall classification accuracy of the 2005 map is more than 90\% \cite{roy_development_2015}. The 1985 and 1995 maps were not explicitly tested due to a lack of historical ground truth points. The 2005 map was used as the basis for statistical analysis and initialising the land change model and the 1985 and 1995 maps were used for evaluating the simulated land use/land cover maps. \\

